
" aimed at producing effects while typing the code; e.g. to type
**xyz**, type ,bxyz  ( means the ESC key), as opposed to first
typing xyz, then highlighting it, then making is bold

" insert URL link
map! ,u []()2hi

" insert URL image link
map! ,mgu ![alt text]()i

" insert local image location
map! ,mgl ![loc]()i

" insert italicized tex
map! ,i **i

" insert bold tex
map! ,b ****hi

" insert displayed R code
map! ,rc ``` r```ki

